## 4. Keamanan & Sinkronisasi (Routes & Controllers)

### Route Produk ([backend/routes/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/routes/products.js))
**PENTING**: Pastikan route `PUT` dan `DELETE` menggunakan `auth` agar `req.userId` tersedia.

```javascript
router.put('/:id', auth, addUserInfo, handleFileUpload, updateProduct);
```

### Integrasi Sinkronisasi
Panggil [syncProductWithCashflow](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/utils/cashflowHelper.js#5-98) pada:
1. [controllers/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js) -> [createProduct](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js#96-223) (setelah `.save()`)
2. [controllers/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js) -> [updateProduct](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js#381-582) (setelah `.save()`)
3. [routes/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/routes/products.js) -> `/import-document-save` (di dalam loop simpan)
4. [routes/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/routes/products.js) -> `/import-corrected-word` (saat update/promote produk)

---

## 5. Filter Database ([backend/controllers/products.js](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js))

Tambahkan filter berikut pada fungsi [getProducts](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/backend/controllers/products.js#224-315):
```javascript
const { paymentStatus, hasPrice } = req.query;
if (paymentStatus) query.paymentStatus = paymentStatus;
if (hasPrice === 'true') query.harga = { $gt: 0 };
```

---

## 6. Tips Agar Tidak Error
1. **Model Check**: Pastikan model [Cashflow](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/frontend/src/components/CashflowManagement.js#19-720) memiliki field `productId` dengan type `ObjectId`.
2. **Auth Consistency**: Jika `req.userId` kosong, sinkronisasi cashflow akan gagal saat mencoba menyimpan field `createdBy`. Selalu gunakan middleware `auth`.
3. **Currency Conversion**: Di frontend, selalu gunakan [cleanCurrency()](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/frontend/src/utils/formatHelpers.js#16-27) sebelum mengirim data harga ke backend untuk menghindari error tipe data [Number](file:///Users/macbook/projects/kue_lapis/frontend/src/components/Dashboard.js#511-514).
